# SQL warehouses & serverless

- **SQL warehouse** — compute tuned for SQL & BI: powers Databricks SQL, dashboards, BI tools
- **Three kinds** — Classic & Pro (your account), Serverless (Databricks account, instant)
- **Autoscaling** — a warehouse adds clusters to absorb query concurrency
- **Serverless** — a modality across SQL, jobs, notebooks & pipelines: seconds to start, no idle cost
- **Trade** — less network control for speed + zero cluster management
